            <title><![CDATA[파키스탄 정부 “대홍수로 이재민 3300만명 발생”]]></title>
            <link>https://www.khan.co.kr/world/asia-australia/article/202208262100001/?utm_campaign=list_click&amp;utm_source=reporter_article&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=%EB%B0%95%EC%9D%80%ED%95%98_%EA%B8%B0%EC%9E%90%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80</link>
